<div id="review_2959671306" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2959671306" />
    <a title="Ricky McConnell" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/93140046-ricky-mcconnell"><img alt="Ricky McConnell" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1563231231p2/93140046.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2959671306?book_show_action=true">Jun 18, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Ricky McConnell" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Ricky McConnell" href="/user/show/93140046-ricky-mcconnell">Ricky McConnell</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/44100452-the-collected-stories-of-arthur-c-clarke">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2959671306" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17410312074794966325">This was a long collection and it took me a while to get through it. I really enjoyed the stories about the moon. I liked most of the stories, but a few were not good for me. I am a fan of the author and have enjoyed other works that came after this collection. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

