        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3261543662" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7245819530726803582">Because it has all the stories, the collection is naturally a little hit and miss. Yes, at times things skew a little formulaic. But it&apos;s entertaining to see Clarke develop as an author, and to explore a wide variety of premises. Each story is so short and paced quickly so it never drags. For those keeping score, Clarke&apos;s mild misogyny, a product of the times, attenuates later in his career. Not an ideal intro to Clarke or golden age sci-fi, but definitely recommended for fans of the author or t</span>
  <span id="freeText7245819530726803582" style="display:none">Because it has all the stories, the collection is naturally a little hit and miss. Yes, at times things skew a little formulaic. But it's entertaining to see Clarke develop as an author, and to explore a wide variety of premises. Each story is so short and paced quickly so it never drags. For those keeping score, Clarke's mild misogyny, a product of the times, attenuates later in his career. Not an ideal intro to Clarke or golden age sci-fi, but definitely recommended for fans of the author or the genre.</span>
  <a data-text-id="7245819530726803582" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

